680
00:40:09,076 --> 00:40:12,246
Lähme otsime kusagilt süüa.
- Kuhu sa minna tahad?

681
00:40:12,412 --> 00:40:14,039
Sinna, kuhu sina tahad.

682
00:40:14,206 --> 00:40:17,793
Vaata seda ilusat rohelist.

683
