695
00:41:19,646 --> 00:41:20,772
Jah?

696
00:41:24,109 --> 00:41:26,778
Ma pean sinna
paariks päevaks tagasi minema.

697
00:41:26,945 --> 00:41:28,405
Ei.

698
00:41:28,572 --> 00:41:31,033
Kahju küll,
aga see on lihtsalt uus äri.

699
00:41:32,743 --> 00:41:36,205
Niipea, kui selle käima saab,
olen kogu aeg kodus.

700
00:41:36,371 --> 00:41:39,500
Ma luban. Eks ole?

701
00:41:41,502 --> 00:41:43,086
